Sir, what's the sum total of your daughters?

734
00:50:39,120 --> 00:50:39,990
空的  沒有支票
Empty. No gift cheques.

735
00:50:40,330 --> 00:50:42,410
怎么把支票忘了  拉賈...法爾漢
Forgot the cheques, Raju...Farhan?

736
00:50:42,500 --> 00:50:46,660
我們沒邀請你  你們是新郎的客人吧
We didn't invite you, you must be from the groom's side.

737
00:50:47,160 --> 00:50:51,120
不  校長  我們代表著科學而來
No sir, we're here as the emissaries of science.

738
00:50:51,250 --> 00:50:53,450
什么意思  你能解釋一下嗎
How? Can you explain?

739
00:50:53,700 --> 00:50:55,380
爸爸  他這么能言善辯
Dad, he explains superbly.

740
00:50:55,380 --> 00:50:57,370
我相信他會給我們一個解釋的
I'm sure he'll give us a demo.

741
00:50:57,660 --> 00:50:58,620
對吧
Won't you?

742
00:50:59,450 --> 00:51:03,040
新德里經常發生停電...
Well, Delhi has plenty of power cuts that...

743
