這會打斷婚禮的行進
Disrupt wedding celebrations.

744
00:51:05,950 --> 00:51:08,080
所以我想造個能從客人的汽車里抽取電能
So I thought of making an inverter that

745
00:51:08,200 --> 00:51:10,620
的換流器
draws power from guests' cars.

746
