So where's the inverter?

748
00:51:16,500 --> 00:51:18,120
校長  設計圖已經完成了的
Sir, the design is ready.

749
00:51:21,200 --> 00:51:22,490
設計圖在哪兒呢  法爾漢
Where's the design, Farhan?

750
00:51:22,910 --> 00:51:25,950
-我把它給你了的  -我給了拉賈
- I gave you the design - I gave it to Raju.

751
