Raju, design?

752
00:51:30,410 --> 00:51:34,160
別管設計圖了  我會造出換流器給你看
Never mind the design. I'll make the inverter and show you.

753
00:51:34,500 --> 00:51:38,160
你只會造謠  哪會造什么換流器啊
You can only invent stories, not an inverter.

754
00:51:38,450 --> 00:51:41,540
