And I'll name it after you.

756
00:51:44,500 --> 00:51:48,570
畢竟  這是在你女兒的婚禮上發明的
After all, it was invented at your daughter's wedding.

757
00:51:48,570 --> 00:51:49,290
很榮幸...
So it'll be an honor...

758
00:51:49,410 --> 00:51:55,450
