Sir, what was the cost per plate? We'll reimburse you.

760
00:52:05,160 --> 00:52:06,830
...不過得按揭
...in instailments.

761
00:52:09,290 --> 00:52:11,050
我們絕不會再亂闖婚禮了
We'll never crash a wedding again.

762
00:52:11,050 --> 00:52:12,540
哪怕是我們自己的婚禮
Not even my own.

763
00:52:12,660 --> 00:52:14,910
事實上  我甚至不會結婚  他也不會
In fact, I won't even marry. Nor will he.

764
00:52:15,580 --> 00:52:17,620
對...不結婚
Uh...right. No marriage.

765
00:52:19,120 --> 00:52:21,490
你們的父母也不該結婚
Your parents shouldn't have married either.

766
00:52:23,160 --> 00:52:25,700
