The world would have to feed two less idiots.

767
00:52:28,200 --> 00:52:29,240
坐下
Sit!

768
00:52:40,250 --> 00:52:41,290
聽好了
Pay attention.

769
00:52:52,200 --> 00:52:57,160
這是蘭柯霍達斯父親的月收入
This is Ranchhoddas's father's monthly income.

770
00:52:58,500 --> 00:53:04,830
去掉兩個零也還是一筆可觀的收入
Couple of zeroes less, and it's still a sizeable income.

771
00:53:07,370 --> 00:53:13,700
但是再去掉一個零  我就有點擔心了
But erase another zero, and I would worry a little.

772
00:53:14,950 --> 00:53:18,330
這不是你爸爸的收入嗎  法爾漢
Isn't that your fathers income, Farhan?

773
00:53:19,200 --> 00:53:20,910
是的  校長
Yes, sir.

774
00:53:22,290 --> 00:53:24,330
再去掉一個零
Now take away another zero.

775
00:53:27,370 --> 00:53:31,160
就變成你全家的收入了  賈·瑞絲奇
And that's your family income, Raju Rastogi.

776
00:53:32,330 --> 00:53:33,700
真讓人擔心啊
Big reason to worry.

777
00:53:38,410 --> 00:53:45,580
接受我的建議  搬去跟查特·雷曼寧甘一起住
Take my advice and shift into Chatur Ramalingam's room.

778
00:53:46,000 --> 00:53:47,300
馬上要考試了
Exams are here.

779
00:53:47,300 --> 00:53:50,240
你們再跟蘭柯混下去肯定不及格
Stay with Rancho and you're sure to fail.

780
00:54:12,160 --> 00:54:14,580
-要刮胡子嗎  -不用  校長
- Want a shave? - No, sir.

781
00:54:14,750 --> 00:54:15,620
那還不快滾
Then get lost!

782
00:54:26,870 --> 00:54:29,700
別擔心  拉賈
Raju, don't worry.

783
00:54:29,700 --> 00:54:32,450
病毒想要分裂我們  分而治之
This is Virus's move to split us. Divide and rule.

784
00:54:32,580 --> 00:54:33,660
我不得不擔心
I have to worry.

785
00:54:34,080 --> 00:54:35,410
他給我們打分
He grades us,

786
00:54:35,410 --> 00:54:37,580
我需要個好分數來找個好工作
and I need good grades for a good job

787
00:54:38,500 --> 00:54:41,540
我們不像你  有個有錢的爸爸
Unlike you, I don't have a rich Dad I can live off.

788
00:54:41,660 --> 00:54:43,540
閉嘴  拉賈
Shut up, Raju.

789
00:54:43,790 --> 00:54:46,450
我們非要聽他的廢話嗎  平安無事
Must we follow all his hogwash? 'aal izz well'

790
00:54:46,830 --> 00:54:48,290
我才不會像你一樣當他的跟班
I won't be his flunky like you.

791
00:54:49,250 --> 00:54:50,280
你有點過分了
You're crossing the line.

792
00:54:50,280 --> 00:54:51,540
不  我是在畫好界限
No, I'm drawing one.

793
00:54:52,040 --> 00:54:53,740
我要養家糊口
I have a family to support.

794
00:54:55,950 --> 00:54:58,200
我爸的醫藥費花光了我媽的退休金
Dad's medicines swallow up Mom's pension.

795
00:55:00,160 --> 00:55:04,540
我姐嫁不出去  因為他們要一輛車做嫁妝
My sis can't marry because they want a car in dowry.

796
00:55:07,450 --> 00:55:11,700
我媽已經5年沒買過一件新的紗麗服了
Mom hasn't bought a single saree in five years

797
00:55:14,540 --> 00:55:17,740
不要把你媽的衣柜也扯到這個問題里來
Now don't get your Mom's wardrobe into the debate.

798
00:55:18,870 --> 00:55:20,870
順便問下  一年買幾件紗麗服才正常
By the way, how many sarees per annum is reasonable?

799
00:55:21,950 --> 00:55:23,200
別開我媽的玩笑
Hey...no wisecracks about Mom.

800
00:55:23,950 --> 00:55:28,200
我們要用心學習  而不是只為求個分數
We'll study with all our heart, but not just for grades.

801
00:55:28,870 --> 00:55:33,200
智者說  學習是以修煉氣質而不為斂財
To quote a wise one -- study to be accomplished, not affluent

802
00:55:33,950 --> 00:55:39,490
以優秀自律  成功自會隨你而來
Follow excellence, and success will chase you, pants down!

803
00:55:40,700 --> 00:55:41,710
哪個智者說過這話
Which wise one says this?

804
00:55:41,710 --> 00:55:43,330
又是精神領袖蘭柯霍達斯?
His holiness guru Ranchhoddas?

805
00:55:45,370 --> 00:55:46,370
別扯淡了
Go rot in the bogs!

806
00:55:48,000 --> 00:55:50,990
拉賈  放輕松  我們會考第一的  萬事皆有可能
Raju, don't stress. We'll top our class. Nothing is impossible.

807
00:55:51,290 --> 00:55:52,450
萬事皆有可能?  真的嗎
Nothing is impossible? Oh yeah?

808
00:55:56,120 --> 00:55:58,240
塞回管子里
Shove this back into the tube.

809
00:56:01,290 --> 00:56:02,910
拉賈選擇了另一條路
Raju got onto another train.

810
00:56:03,450 --> 00:56:06,040
他在查特手下的悲慘命運開始了
His travails with Chatur began.

811
00:56:06,040 --> 00:56:08,620
沒錯  是悲慘命運  不是快樂的旅程
Yes, I mean travails, not travels.

812
00:56:13,040 --> 00:56:14,950
查特綽號"消音器"
Chatur was called "silencer".

813
00:56:15,290 --> 00:56:17,000
為了歷練自己的記憶力
To sharpen his memory,

814
00:56:17,000 --> 00:56:18,990
