he popped pills from a local quack.

815
00:56:19,410 --> 00:56:21,370
從此以后放屁不出聲  卻奇臭無比
And then let off silent...but lethal farts.

816
00:56:24,080 --> 00:56:27,290
不是我...是拉賈放的吧
I didn't do it...Raju?

817
00:56:27,450 --> 00:56:30,120
自己放屁卻總讓別人背黑鍋
He always blamed others for the output.

818
00:56:30,870 --> 00:56:33,740
消音器每天苦讀18個小時
Silencer crammed 18 hours a day.

819
00:56:34,000 --> 00:56:37,120
考試前夕  則想方設法分散他人注意力
On exam eve, he would distract others.

820
00:56:41,080 --> 00:56:44,160
他堅信--人生登頂之路只有兩條
His belief -- there are only two ways of topping:

821
00:56:44,500 --> 00:56:47,790
抬升自己的分數或者壓低對手的分數
elevate your own grades or shrink your opponents' grades.

822
00:56:52,080 --> 00:56:55,950
蘭柯則想出了絕妙的辦法
Rancho decided to subdue silencer and rescue Raju

823
00:56:56,410 --> 00:56:57,700
來幫助拉賈  消滅"消音器"
with one master plan.

824
00:56:59,750 --> 00:57:04,710
我們的導師孜孜不倦地服務于...
Our director has unceasingly served...

825
00:57:04,710 --> 00:57:07,740
"服務"的意思是...
"served" means...

826
00:57:07,830 --> 00:57:11,870
管他什么意思  記住就行
Damn the meaning, I'll memorize it.

827
00:57:13,290 --> 00:57:16,910
查特負責在教師節那天致詞
Chatur was the introductory speaker at the teachers' day function.

828
00:57:17,250 --> 00:57:19,630
為了給病毒留下深刻印象
To impress Virus,

829
00:57:19,630 --> 00:57:21,160
他找圖書管理員幫忙
he got his speech written by the librarian

830
00:57:21,370 --> 00:57:22,700
寫一篇浮夸絢麗的文章來
in highbrow Hindi.

831
00:57:24,250 --> 00:57:29,620
你好  稍等  查特  有電話
Hello. Hold on. Chatur, call for you.

832
00:57:30,000 --> 00:57:32,410
幫我收一下打印稿  我去去就回
Please collect the printout. I'll be right back.

833
00:57:35,200 --> 00:57:37,080
而我要做的是
Oh...the things I have to do.

834
00:57:40,660 --> 00:57:43,830
杜別先生  校長念叨您呢
Mr. Dubey, the director was remembering you.

835
00:57:43,950 --> 00:57:45,540
-真的嗎  -沒錯  剛還念叨呢
- Really? - Yes. Just now.

836
00:57:45,910 --> 00:57:49,290
我這就去見他  把這個交給查特
I'll see him right away. Give this to Chatur.

837
00:57:54,450 --> 00:57:55,340
你好  喂?
Hello. Hello.

838
00:57:55,340 --> 00:57:57,490
你好  雷曼寧甘先生嗎
Hello, Mr. Ramalingam?

839
00:57:57,620 --> 00:57:58,540
什么事啊
Yes?

840
00:57:59,120 --> 00:58:01,490
這里是警察局
I'm calling from the police station.

841
00:58:01,870 --> 00:58:04,700
-你是烏干達來的嗎  -是的  長官
- Are you from Uganda? - Yes, sir.

842
00:58:06,250 --> 00:58:07,920
你現在有生命危險
Your life is in danger.

843
00:58:07,920 --> 00:58:09,290
什么  怎么回事
What? How?

844
00:58:10,410 --> 00:58:12,200
