Listen carefully, or else...

845
00:58:12,830 --> 00:58:17,160
你一邁出校門就得一命嗚呼
You'll get killed as you step out of the college gate.

846
00:58:17,910 --> 00:58:19,160
為什么  出什么事了
Why? What happened?

847
00:58:19,290 --> 00:58:20,870
查特被纏住的當兒
While Chatur was kept engaged,

848
00:58:21,290 --> 00:58:24,900
