Rancho altered a few words in his speech,

849
00:58:24,910 --> 00:58:27,870
比如  把"服務"改成"壓榨"
for eg, 'served' became 'screwed'.

850
00:58:28,700 --> 00:58:29,990
校長在嗎
Yes, sir?

851
00:58:30,540 --> 00:58:33,080
-你是誰  -我叫杜別  圖書管理員
- Who are you? - Dubey. Librarian.

852
