I'm permanent staff, sir.

853
00:58:37,450 --> 00:58:38,870
恭喜你
Congratulations.

854
00:58:39,290 --> 00:58:42,660
等一下  警長在和我通話
Hold on a moment. The chief is on the other line.

855
00:58:43,040 --> 00:58:43,990
喂?  你好
Excuse me, sir

856
00:58:53,660 --> 00:58:55,910
那...我該去哪兒呢
Yes...so where was I?

857
00:58:56,160 --> 00:58:58,580
你說我死定了...只要一出校門
You said I may die...outside the gate.

858
00:58:58,700 --> 00:59:05,120
沒錯  你一出大門就會看見紅綠燈
Right. As you get out of the gate, you'll see a traffic signal.

859
00:59:05,330 --> 00:59:07,370
紅綠燈  好的
Traffic signal. Ok.

860
00:59:07,580 --> 00:59:13,120
