When it turns red, all the cars will halt.

861
00:59:13,620 --> 00:59:14,950
對  然后呢
Ok. Then?

862
00:59:15,080 --> 00:59:17,080
小心翼翼地穿過馬路
Then cross the road with great caution.

863
00:59:17,830 --> 00:59:22,120
因為孩子  在高峰時段被車撞的話
Because son, in rush hour if a car hits you,

864
00:59:22,120 --> 00:59:23,080
就死定了
you're dead.

865
00:59:25,000 --> 00:59:26,830
扯淡  我知道啊
What nonsense! I know that.

866
00:59:26,950 --> 00:59:30,540
你知道了  好的  這樣你安全了
You know that? Excellent. Then you're safe my boy.

867
00:59:37,580 --> 00:59:39,660
管理員給你的  消音器
From the librarian, silencer.

868
00:59:39,790 --> 00:59:41,370
不許那么叫我  昌恰德
You don't call me that, Chanchad.

869
00:59:47,200 --> 00:59:49,290
校長說他沒找過我
Hey. The director said he didn't call for me.

870
00:59:50,080 --> 00:59:52,330
誰說他找你了  我是說他念叨你呢
Who said 'called'? I just said he 'remembered' you.

871
00:59:52,500 --> 00:59:55,080
念叨?  你個淘氣包
Remembered? Rascais!

872
