尊敬的主席先生
Distinguished Mr. Chairperson.

873
01:00:07,580 --> 01:00:11,870
各位貴賓  令人敬仰的教育部長
Chief guest, the honorable minister of education.

874
01:00:12,500 --> 01:00:16,450
各位敬愛的老師  同學們
Respected teachers and friends.

875
01:00:18,040 --> 01:00:22,910
ICE的招牌已名揚四海
Ice has now soared beyond the stratosphere.

876
01:00:23,540 --> 01:00:27,830
一切的溢美之詞
The credit goes solely to

877
01:00:28,250 --> 01:00:31,440
卻都涌向韋魯·薩哈斯布達博士
Dr. Viru Sahastrabuddhe.

878
01:00:31,440 --> 01:00:32,040
熱烈歡迎他
Give him a big hand.

879
01:00:32,160 --> 01:00:34,280
校長  聲音是他的
Sir, the voice is his

880
01:00:34,280 --> 01:00:36,200
可講稿卻出自我之手啊
but the words are mine.

881
01:00:36,950 --> 01:00:39,200
他是一個偉人  您名副其實
He's a great guy, really you are.

